            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Cornelius Rufus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> augur <expan><abbr>mun</abbr><ex>icipii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Vim</abbr><ex>inacii</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>vixit <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> LXX <lb n="5"/>Ulpia Rufina uxor et <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Corn</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan> Pacatus <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fl</abbr><ex>amen</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>mun</abbr><ex>icipii</ex></expan> eiusdem et <lb n="8"/>Corneliae Rufina et <lb n="9"/>Bassa <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex cert="low">ii</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>hered</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>ene</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erenti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uraverunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb und unterhalb des Inschriftfeldes figürliche Reliefdarstellungen: Frau und Krieger an der Stadtmauer (Helena und Menelaos?); Tierfries mit Hunde, Pferd und Eber; zwei Liktoren und sella curulis. (B): Milovanović: Z. 7/8: Zeilenfall nicht angegeben.</p>
            </div>
